        "timestamp": "2018-11-17 14:52:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI am going to get clarification on this from the list - as several projects music, vfc for example are already doing this\nhttps://git.onap.org/music/distributed-kv-store/tree/deployment/Dockerfile",
